<h1><strong>Devour the Burger, yum</strong></h1>

<h3>Add a Burger or Devour one!</h3>

<h4><strong><u>de·vour:</u></strong><em> dəˈvou(ə)</em> <em><strong> verb</strong></em>
eat (food or prey) hungrily or quickly.
"he devoured half of his burger in one bite"
synonyms:	eat hungrily, eat greedily, gobble (up/down), guzzle, gulp (down), bolt (down), gorge oneself on, wolf (down), feast on, consume, eat up</h4>

